p;rft.date=2010&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1002%2Fjclp.20681&amp;rft.aulast=Werth&amp;rft.aufirst=J.L.&amp;rft.au=Hastings%2C+S.L.&amp;rft.au=Riding-Malon%2C+R.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADual+relationship\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://socialworkers.org/pubs/code/code.asp\">\"Code of Ethics\"</a>. National Association of Social Workers. p.&#160;Section 1.02.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Code+of+Ethics&amp;rft.pages=Section+1.02&amp;rft.pub=National+Association+of+Social+Workers&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsocialworkers.org%2Fpubs%2Fcode%2Fcode.asp&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADual+relationship\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1253\nCached time: 20180909000212\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.080 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.102 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 313/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 10011/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 81/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 7094/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.043/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.4 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   83.898      1 Template:Reflist\n100.00%   83.898      1 -total\n 57.34%   48.105      3 Template:Cite_web\n 24.66%   20.692      4 Template:Cite_journal\n  2.03%    1.703      1 Tem